{"tid":853331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★靈異！】無人操作！支國iphone自動打開微信代訂萬元總統套房、火車票","createTime":"2018-10-08T13:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T03:13:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b1e287ac963cf509469e17f45931c4a77e10755","tid":853331,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"浙江一女士稱用山寨充電頭充電，差點自動預定萬元酒店<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10月6日，錢江晚報發布了一則標題為《什麼鬼！ 正充電的手機，自動訂了萬元總統套房》的報導。 浙江楊女士用山寨的充電頭及充電線為蘋果手機充電的過程中，<span style=\"color: red;\">手機自動打開了攜程APP軟件並預定了萬元的總統套房</span>。 當手機跳轉微信支付頁面的時候，楊女士拔掉了充電線，才終止了操作。<br />\n<br />\n另據報導中楊女士的介紹，此前手機還自動點進了微信讀書，並在東野圭吾的作品下打了不少書評。 據楊女士展示書評截圖顯示，其中有漢字也有英文亂碼。 此外，還曾出現<span style=\"color: red;\">手機自動訂火車票的情況，當手機正在勾選乘車人時，楊女士發現並及時將其關閉。</span><br />\n<br />\n深圳一女士稱手機打開企業微信並輸入英文字符<br />\n<br />\n10月7日，深圳的吳女士向南都記者反映，她也遇到了此前報導中出現的類似情況。 &ldquo;昨天用這個充電頭充電時，發現會出現自動點開程序的操作，並沒有在意。今早看到這個報導後，我又插上手機想試一下，沒想到它自動打開了企業微信，並在一個對話框中輸入了一串英文。&rdquo;據吳女士提供的截圖顯示，該英文內容為&ldquo;You'redov do and gSZ&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;最先輸入了SZ，緊接著有輸入了後面的字符，我等它輸完了以後太害怕了就把充電線拔掉了，操作就終止了。&rdquo;吳女士說。 另據吳女士介紹，該充電頭她也說不上來歷，但不是蘋果原裝配件。 家裡充電頭較多，近日她隨手翻出使用，使用的充電線則為蘋果原裝數據線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.163.com/18/1007/23/DTI7BQDU000187VE.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.163.com%2F18%2F1007%2F23%2FDTI7BQDU000187VE.html&d=4M1Ay0u2QmYh%2BS6rfY5nGi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fc61b8fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.163.com/18/1007/23/DTI7BQDU000187VE.html</a>"},{"pid":"817fb2ee971c57fa680106b5f46771e0b827e973","tid":853331,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b91e77f8b2e8c3184de1190c68cd72c4305ae8","tid":853331,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"用家問題好似係"},{"pid":"93e5050e95cfdf0ad30aa6a9ff488f94bec61da0","tid":853331,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"好新聞咩？<br />\n華強北 行一轉，大把人掛牌公然賣黑客程式<br />\n初時唔為意，以為電訊公司sales<br />\n望清楚個掛牌，心裏涼了一截<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d95becf207f4c20a3cb7e12b49e13ffe2deaa9","tid":853331,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"老貓有v7 pay, 會幫你做pornhub付費會員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5333bab499110668a368a78870f2436a112e33d","tid":853331,"uid":3331,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T17:33:09.000Z","msg":"似係部iPhone接電之後電容出問題<br />\n個支那婆吹到訂埋酒店識打評論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊有黑客咁on9偷野偷到咁樣樣<br />\n偷偷地係backstage偷完就走啦"},{"pid":"80c65d48d4c41ab71fb1645264189b9f734754c4","tid":853331,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"iPhone usb 0day 漏洞咁值錢<br />\n會淨係拎去book房咁簡單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864f24392be012f4a7b37f6611ed2840ae4bbf52","tid":853331,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"爆到iPhone發達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲寫書評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53b6b8b6bcce64ce35bcee2f4f1e26e2a8b8ef2","tid":853331,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 弱智標題"},{"pid":"1ed6ea4b65fc318ba2b6377b8b55531f22550